    "Early female art historian of the Italian Renaissance; author of the first systematic study of Christian iconography in the English language.": [],
    "Born the daughter of the Irish miniaturist painter Denis Murphy and English wife (name now lost), the family emigrated to England in 1798, finally settling in London in 1803.": [
